Present in Qld, Tas and Vic. |
| Helionothrips errans        | None                                              | Feeds on many orchid species, potentially causing serious damage to leaves. |
| Heliothrips haemorrhoidalis | Greenhouse thrips                                 | Feeds on a wide range of trees and shrubs, including ferns, tea, Pinus spp. Feeds on older leaves, particularly of plants that are stressed. Widespread throughout Australia. |
| Hercinothrips bicinctus     | Banana silvering thrips; banded greenhouse thrips | Many host plant species including bananas. Feeds and breeds on leaves.